name: SDXL Upscale Latents Example
author: gogurt enjoyer
description: Sample Stable Diffusion XL workflow for the Upscale Latents node.

data.label: Notes
data.notes:
This is an example SDXL workflow for the Upscale Latents node. Initial width and height should be set to something around 1024, and the larger upscaled size will be determined by the Scale Factor. (i.e. 1024x1024, scale factor 1.25, output image will be 1280x1280).

Also, make sure that your numbers make sense - the final resolution should be divisible by 8 to make Stable Diffusion happy.
